casebody.data:
Turner, Appellant, v. Fowler, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 3, 1890.)

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Smith & Bowman, for appellant. Abbott Bros., for respondent.

No opinion. Motion to dismiss appeal for non-service of printed papers granted, with costs.
